  abstract = {MPI-ESM is a new version of the global Earth system model developed at the Max
Planck Institute for Meteorology. This paper describes the ocean state and circulation
as well as basic aspects of variability in simulations contributing to the fifth phase of
the Coupled Model Intercomparison Project (CMIP5). The performance of the ocean/
